/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbtw,  男既係呢d時刻好少口是心非，簡單d講，佢真係想分手，or佢已經有另一個，想拖住你先，睇下另一條囡岩唔岩key,  唔岩就睇下仲有冇機同返你一齊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢出面無第二個嘅 應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知咖呢啲 話唔埋"},{"pid":"708734b5143da4bb23cd9478e4b061ef37f30048","tid":391764,"uid":145155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"姐係有第二個囉x2"},{"pid":"def21370ccc256fb34bc94ac2c839d6c0bb5024c","tid":391764,"uid":86098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"好聽嘅咪叫做分開下，冷靜一排，大家仲適唔適合大家。<br />\n通常男仔講岀口，都無彎轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:年頭比前度飛，又係講冷靜下(拍左6年，開埋聯名户口)。兩個星期後佢同左另一個男仔一齊。早啲望清楚一個人，好過第時後悔。依家識到個好愛我嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下個會更好，無謂原地踏步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}